          aboutstressinfo:"Stress (tension) is understood as a set of non-specific adaptive reactions of the body to the influence of various unfavorable factors (physical or psychological). All processes in the human body are subject to psychoemotional state. The appearance of stress in the human body disrupts homeostasis, the state of the nervous system, etc.",
          hans:"HANS SELLE'S RESEARCH",
